keria(89) red,one-shoulder <p>The handkerchief hem is key for SS17 and the white and black striped Rhoni dress is a fresh take on the look. Beautifully flattering in silhouette, it features a ruffle front detail and a gathered waist panel, and it falls to a figure-skimming midi-length skirt with an asymmetric hem. Wear it with strappy heeled sandals come summer.</p>